WEBVTT

00:00:00.373 --> 00:00:02.690
Chris Anderson: I get now to introduce

00:00:02.714 --> 00:00:05.500
one of the most powerful
women in the world.

00:00:05.524 --> 00:00:10.744
I mean, if we are to escape
from the mess that we're in right now,

00:00:10.768 --> 00:00:14.728
she is going to play a major part
in helping us do that.

00:00:15.514 --> 00:00:17.896
She's the head of
the International Monetary Fund,

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:22.013
a delight to welcome here
Kristalina Georgieva.

00:00:24.387 --> 00:00:25.570
Kristalina, welcome.

00:00:25.594 --> 00:00:27.950
Kristalina Georgieva:
Great to be with you, Chris.

00:00:27.974 --> 00:00:29.593
Thank you for having me.

00:00:29.617 --> 00:00:32.839
CA: So you just took on
this role late last year,